# Google OAuth 2.0 client ID (Web application) for GIS / signInWithIdToken.
# Optional: if unset, the app falls back to Supabase redirect-based Google OAuth.
# Get it from Google Cloud Console → APIs & Services → Credentials → OAuth 2.0 Client ID.
# Add Authorized JavaScript origins: https://your-domain.github.io, http://localhost:5173
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
